name: Henloween Ugliness
description:
The Late Henloween Drop.

This drop is to celebrate the Halloween event with Hicetnunc. 

This artwork is about a reminder of me and us that the beauty privilege is still up in the lateness of 2021. The horror part is that society is still tend to love the fake and ditch the real one who always says the truth. If we want to speak up and let people hear out our voice, first: beautify ourselves.

Rework of watercolour on paper on digital editing.
Happy Halloween 2021.
